<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently, the router has many flaws and drawbacks, which this refactoring is going to solve. This includes usability of the router, as well as performance and code-cleaning. Will be worked out with a mini proposal post 1.8.</p>

<p>This issue is to be solved with ZF 2.0, as it involves many BC-breaks. A quick and short list of possible changes:</p>

<ul><li>Removing getInstance(), instead __construct($options)</li>
<li>Making getDefaults(), getDefault() of routes interface methods</li>
<li>Making getCurrentRoute() and getCurrentRouteName() interface methods</li>
<li>CS Cleanup</li>
<li>Using match(Zend_Controller_Request_Http $request) in the interface</li>
<li>Allowing request-method routing per route</li>
</ul>
